                            <comment id="12628771" author="streamy" created="Fri, 5 Sep 2008 22:33:21 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Per discussion with Jim, I added a stopProxy boolean flag to HCM.deleteConnectionInfo that is passed to close() to determine whether we should stop the proxy or not.&lt;/p&gt;

